Ormat Wins Partial Guarantee for $350 Million Geothermal Project

-- B y   T o d d   W h i t e
-- 
2011-06-09T16:31:52Z

-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2011-06-09/ormat-wins-partial-guarantee-for-350-million-geothermal-project.html
Ormat Technologies Inc. (ORA)  said in a
statement that a unit won a conditional commitment from the U.S.
government to partially guarantee as much as $350 million in
loans for a geothermal power project in  Nevada . The subsidiary,
Ormat Nevada Inc., received an offer of conditional commitment
from the  Department of Energy , according to the statement.  To contact the editor responsible for this story:
Todd White at 
 twhite2@bloomberg.net  